find all process containing port 3000 - 
ps -ef | grep 3000

kill the above process 
kill -9 <pid>

run a process in the background
put a & sign at the last of the command.

node node_modules/http-server/bin/http-server -p 3000 &

Using forever -
forever start node_modules/http-server/bin/http-server -p 3000
